 <text>
  <front>
   <head>Sent as from a School-fellow to my Son Anno 1727.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">to see you waste your Time,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And turn your Thoughts so much to Rhyme,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Be wise â€” your useless Views resign,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And fly the fair, delusive</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">, they try their wonted Art,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">To win your easy, youthful Heart;</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">They talk of an immortal Name,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And promise you the Realms of Fame:</l>
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">A mighty Empire,  'tis true,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But wondrous small the Revenue!</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">tell you too, to gain their Ends,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">That Verse will raise you pow'rful Friends.</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Believe me, Youth, this is not true:</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The  think ev'ry Thing their</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
